501
01:19:36,123 --> 01:19:37,239
<i>Alo.</i>

502
01:19:38,667 --> 01:19:40,079
<i>Benim.</i>

503
01:19:41,837 --> 01:19:43,083
<i>Dwight Evans.</i>

504
01:19:44,756 --> 01:19:47,165
